# Branch: main. Bumped 2026-06-03 from 7249c61 to land the reference-taint
# prune convergence fix. _scan_variant_refs now resets `cur` on the
# un-suffixed `void <name>(CpuState*)` entry-point aliases emit_bank appends
# after each bank's bodies; previously every alias's forwarding call was
# attributed to the LAST real variant body in the bank, falsely tainting it,
# and pruning that body shifted the victim to the next so the prune never
# reached a fixpoint (the SMW/ALttP regen treadmill). Companion: codegen
# emits one-line dispatch case/default even with pre_call (keeps the runtime
# (m,x) switch out of the direct-reference graph); v2_regen gets a fixed
# 1.5h wall-clock cap + non-convergence backstops + rolling prune snapshots.
# All 3 games (SMW/ALttP/MMX) regen-converge and build against this commit;
# user-verified playing correctly. No SMW rebuild required for this bump.
